Cactus Code Thorn RecoverMarti
Thorn Author(s)     : Tanja Bode <tbode@gravity.psu.edu>
Thorn Maintainer(s) : Tanja Bode <tbode@gravity.psu.edu>
--------------------------------------------------------------------------

Purpose of the thorn:

Provide a simplified recovery of the primitives from the Whisky conservatives
as described by Marti and Mueller in their LLR: Numerical Hydrodynamics in 
Special Relativity.
